cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on image coding using object-based segmentation and compression, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for image compression also falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The end-to-end learning framework and optimization of components suggest a focus on deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
